    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. The relative hemolysis index predictions satisfy the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all five operating points with a maximum deviation of 11.4% against experimental data, well within the ±20% tolerance. The assessment package is therefore accepted as sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision.",
